---
import Layout from "@/layouts/main.astro"
import SiteHeader from "@/components/site-header"
import SiteFooter from "@/components/site-footer.astro"
---

<Layout
  title="Модул: Транспорт — Veridex ERP"
  description="Тури, налози и оперативно планирање. Поврзете возила, возачи и нарачки во едноставен работен тек."
>
  <SiteHeader client:load currentPath="/moduli/transport" />

  <main class="pt-24">
    <section class="relative overflow-hidden py-16 md:py-24">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/5 via-transparent to-[oklch(0.48_0.22_275_/_0.05)]"></div>
      <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6">
        <div class="max-w-3xl">
          <div class="mb-4 inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-primary/10 px-4 py-1.5 text-sm font-semibold text-primary">
            <span class="flex h-6 w-6 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-primary text-xs font-bold text-white">2</span>
            Модул
          </div>
          <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl">
            Транспортот
            <span class="text-gradient"> под контрола</span>
          </h1>
          <p class="mt-6 max-w-2xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
            Организацијата ви ги дава возилата и луѓето. Транспортниот модул
            ги поврзува &mdash; тури, налози, нарачки, сè на едно место.
          </p>
          <a href="/kontakt" class="mt-8 inline-block">
            <button class="rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-[oklch(0.48_0.22_275)] px-8 py-3.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-lg shadow-primary/25 transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-105">
              Закажи демо
            </button>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-20 md:py-28">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6">
        <div class="mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-tight md:text-4xl">Што вклучува</h2>
          <p class="mt-4 max-w-2xl text-lg text-muted-foreground">
            Оперативното срце на транспортниот бизнис &mdash; планирање
            и извршување на тури.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2">
          <!-- Тури -->
          <div class="rounded-2xl border border-border/50 bg-white p-8">
            <div class="mb-5 flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-primary/10">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 6.75V15m6-6v8.25m.503 3.498 4.875-2.437c.381-.19.622-.58.622-1.006V4.82c0-.836-.88-1.38-1.628-1.006l-3.869 1.934c-.317.159-.69.159-1.006 0L9.503 3.252a1.125 1.125 0 0 0-1.006 0L3.622 5.689C3.24 5.88 3 6.27 3 6.695V19.18c0 .836.88 1.38 1.628 1.006l3.869-1.934c.317-.159.69-.159 1.006 0l4.994 2.497c.317.158.69.158 1.006 0Z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="mb-3 text-xl font-bold">Тури</h3>
            <p class="mb-4 leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
              Секоја тура поврзува возило, приколка, возач и втор возач.
              Знаете точно кој вози каде, со што и кога.
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground">
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><div class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary"></div>Доделување на возило и приколка</li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><div class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary"></div>Возач и втор возач</li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><div class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary"></div>Поврзани трошоци и влезни фактури</li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><div class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary"></div>Документи по тура</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <!-- Налози / Нарачки -->
          <div class="rounded-2xl border border-border/50 bg-white p-8">
            <div class="mb-5 flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-primary/10">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12h3.75M9 15h3.75M9 18h3.75m3 .75H18a2.25 2.25 0 0 0 2.25-2.25V6.108c0-1.135-.845-2.098-1.976-2.192a48.424 48.424 0 0 0-1.123-.08m-5.801 0c-.065.21-.1.433-.1.664 0 .414.336.75.75.75h4.5a.75.75 0 0 0 .75-.75 2.25 2.25 0 0 0-.1-.664m-5.8 0A2.251 2.251 0 0 1 13.5 2.25H15c1.012 0 1.867.668 2.15 1.586m-5.8 0c-.376.023-.75.05-1.124.08C9.095 4.01 8.25 4.973 8.25 6.108V8.25m0 0H4.875c-.621 0-1.125.504-1.125 1.125v11.25c0 .621.504 1.125 1.125 1.125h9.75c.621 0 1.125-.504 1.125-1.125V9.375c0-.621-.504-1.125-1.125-1.125H8.25ZM6.75 12h.008v.008H6.75V12Zm0 3h.008v.008H6.75V15Zm0 3h.008v.008H6.75V18Z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="mb-3 text-xl font-bold">Налози за тури</h3>
            <p class="mb-4 leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
              Нарачки поврзани со секоја тура. Секој налог со свои трошоци
              и излезни фактури &mdash; знаете точно колку заработивте.
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground">
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><div class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary"></div>Нарачки по тура</li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><div class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary"></div>Поврзани трошоци по налог</li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><div class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary"></div>Излезни фактури за наплата</li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><div class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary"></div>Документи и прилози</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- How it connects -->
        <div class="mt-16 rounded-2xl border border-border/50 bg-muted/30 p-8 md:p-10">
          <h3 class="mb-4 text-xl font-bold">Како се поврзува со другите модули</h3>
          <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="mt-0.5 flex h-8 w-8 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-primary/10">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 4.5 21 12m0 0-7.5 7.5M21 12H3" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="text-sm font-semibold">Од Организација</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">Ги повлекува возилата, приколките и вработените за доделување на тури</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="mt-0.5 flex h-8 w-8 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-primary/10">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 4.5 21 12m0 0-7.5 7.5M21 12H3" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="text-sm font-semibold">Кон Финансии</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">Трошоците и фактурите од тури автоматски се појавуваат во финансискиот модул</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="mt-0.5 flex h-8 w-8 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-primary/10">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19.5 14.25v-2.625a3.375 3.375 0 0 0-3.375-3.375h-1.5A1.125 1.125 0 0 1 13.5 7.125v-1.5a3.375 3.375 0 0 0-3.375-3.375H8.25m2.25 0H5.625c-.621 0-1.125.504-1.125 1.125v17.25c0 .621.504 1.125 1.125 1.125h12.75c.621 0 1.125-.504 1.125-1.125V11.25a9 9 0 0 0-9-9Z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="text-sm font-semibold">Документи</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">Секоја тура и налог може да има свои прикачени документи</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-muted/30 py-20 md:py-28">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-tight md:text-4xl">
          Подготвени за транспорт
          <span class="text-gradient"> без хаос?</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="mx-auto mt-6 max-w-xl text-lg text-muted-foreground">
          Видете го модулот во акција со бесплатна демонстрација.
        </p>
        <a href="/kontakt" class="mt-8 inline-block">
          <button class="group relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-[oklch(0.48_0.22_275)] px-10 py-4 text-lg font-semibold text-white shadow-2xl shadow-primary/30 transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-105">
            <span class="relative z-10">Закажи бесплатно демо</span>
            <div class="animate-shimmer absolute inset-0 -z-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-white/20 to-transparent"></div>
          </button>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <SiteFooter />
</Layout>
